This stone resembles a tiger’s eye gemstone, with shimmering bands of brown, gold, and orange glimmering along its surface.

A Scholar’s Stone.

Each stone holds 3 charges. As an action while you are holding the stone, you can use a charge to cast Scholar’s Touch on one creature within view, the effect of the spell lasts 1 hour, rather than the usual 1 minute, or until it is dispelled. All 3 charges are replenished each dawn.

